# AI Resume Ranker

An AI-powered full-stack web application that ranks uploaded resumes based on semantic similarity to a job description using **sentence-transformers** (`all-MiniLM-L6-v2`).

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Tech |
|---|---|
| Frontend | React 18 + Tailwind CSS v3 (Vite) |
| Backend | Python FastAPI |
| AI Model | sentence-transformers `all-MiniLM-L6-v2` |
| File Parsing | pdfplumber + PyPDF2 (PDF), python-docx (DOCX) |
| Similarity | Cosine similarity via scikit-learn |

