## API Reference

### `POST /upload`

Accepts multipart form data:

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `job_description` | `string` | The job description text |
| `files` | `File[]` | One or more resume files (PDF/DOCX/TXT) |

**Response:**
```json
{
  "results": [
    {
      "rank": 1,
      "name": "John Doe",
      "score": 92.4,
      "skills": ["Python", "React", "AWS", "Docker"],
      "filename": "abc123_john_doe_resume.pdf",
      "original_filename": "john_doe_resume.pdf"
    }
  ]
}
```

### `GET /download/{filename}`

Downloads a previously uploaded resume file.

