## Features

- 🤖 **AI Semantic Ranking** – Uses transformer embeddings (not just keyword matching)
- 📁 **Drag & Drop Upload** – Upload multiple PDF/DOCX files at once
- 🏆 **Top Candidate Spotlight** – Gold-highlighted #1 match
- 📊 **Match Score Bars** – Animated percentage bars with color tiers
- 🏷️ **Skill Detection** – Auto-extracts 80+ technical skills from resumes
- 🔀 **Card / Table View** – Toggle between two result layouts
- 📥 **Resume Download** – One-click download for any ranked resume
- 🌙 **Glassmorphism UI** – Dark mode with gradient backgrounds and blur effects

