## Troubleshooting

**Backend fails with "model download" errors:**  
Ensure you have internet access on first run for the ~80 MB model download.

**Frontend shows "Failed to connect to backend":**  
Make sure the backend is running on `http://localhost:8000` before uploading.

**CORS errors in browser:**  
The backend already has `allow_origins=["*"]` — ensure you're running on `localhost:8000`.

**Resume shows 0% score:**  
The PDF may be image-based (scanned). Currently text-based PDFs are supported.
